  "subject": "cds-ui improvements",
  "commit_message": "cds-ui improvements\n\n- Add lifecycle action bar (Edit → Import DD → Enrich → Publish)\n  to package creation screen with CSS stepper styling\n  - Add DD import modal with ngx-file-drop and bulk-upload to\n  blueprint processor\n  - Wire Enrich and Publish actions to existing\n  PackageCreationService methods\n  - Add blueprint-error-handler.ts to map HTTP errors to\n  user-readable messages\n  - Expose POST /resourcedictionary/definition-bulk route in Node\n  BFF (datasource, service, controller)\n  - Add unmapped variable warning banner to Template & Mapping tab\n  - Rewrite guided tour step descriptions with plain-English\n  explanations\n  - Add dev-server.js for HTTP-only BFF startup (no AAF certs\n  required)\n  - Fix Angular dev proxy to use http://localhost:3000 instead of\n  https\n  - Add Playwright e2e tests for lifecycle bar and\n  unmapped-variable indicator\n  - Fix Deploy/Execute button spacing on package view page\n\nIssue-ID: CCSDK-4205\nChange-Id: Ifffa2d71914c8068076c1ab690cc326736d32232\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
